OL,3,CBoy, 15, dies following crash in
OL,4,CScottish Borders
OL,6,FA 15-year-old boy has died following a
OL,7,Fcrash in the Scottish Borders.
OL,9,FHe was a passenger in a car when it
OL,10,Fwas involved in a collision on the
OL,11,FA701 at Hearthstane near Tweedsmuir.
OL,13,FThe incident happened around 2.40pm on
OL,14,FFriday, 17 April, and involved a black
OL,15,FBMW 530e and a yellow Fiat 500 Abarth.
OL,17,FEmergency services including an air
OL,18,Fambulance attended and a 15-year-old
OL,19,Fwho was a passenger in the Fiat was
OL,20,Fpronounced dead at the scene.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/4
