PN,35302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1776687067
OL,3,CBoy, 15, dies following crash in
OL,4,CScottish Borders
OL,6,FThe 54-year-old male driver of the
OL,7,FFiat and his 21-year-old male
OL,8,Fpassenger were taken to the Royal
OL,9,FInfirmary of Edinburgh with serious
OL,10,Fbut not life-threatening injuries.
OL,12,FThe 27-year-old male driver of the BMW
OL,13,Fand his 26-year-old female passenger
OL,14,Fwere taken to hospital as a
OL,15,Fprecaution. He was subsequently
OL,16,Farrested and released pending further
OL,17,Fenquiries.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/4
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
