OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,354,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1776687067
OL,3,CBoy, 15, dies following crash in
OL,4,CScottish Borders
OL,6,FSergeant Jamie Humpage said: "Our
OL,7,Fthoughts are with the family of the
OL,8,Fboy who died, and they have asked for
OL,9,Fprivacy at what is a very difficult
OL,10,Ftime for them.
OL,12,F"Our enquiries are ongoing to
OL,13,Festablish the full circumstances and
OL,14,Fwe are asking anyone in the area at
OL,15,Fthe time who saw what happened to get
OL,16,Fin touch.
OL,18,F"Please also check any dash-cam
OL,19,Ffootage you have to see if it has
OL,20,Fcaptured something that could assist
OL,21,Fwith our investigation."
